snippet.title: C64 Longplay: Ultimate Wizard
snippet.description:
100 levels, some of which were in the original Wizard game:
Beginner mode:
0:48 Playground
1:16 Shadow Lord
2:00 Wizercise 1 – Climbing
3:00 To Trap A Thief
3:43 Where’s Mario?
4:49 Wizard’s Pet
5:29 Ups and Downs
7:22 Tightrope
8:13 THE….THIEF
8:55 Look Before You Leap

Intermediate:
9:23 Ladder Land
9:45 PURPLE TEMPLE
10:50 Where’s Mario II
12:46 Stairway Circus
13:27 (ouch!)
14:16 Immortal Portal
14:56 Wizercise 2 – Jump & Leap
16:22 Phantom Archer
17:29 WIZARD OLYMPICS I
19:17 Hunting Season is Open!
19:50 Arboretum

Advanced:
20:50 Blast Off
22:13 Run Like Crazy!
23:10 Trojan Horse
24:08 Catacombs I
26:17 Temple of Doom
28:19 The Mines of Mordor
29:41 Gauntlet
30:32 WIZARD OLYMPICS II
Couldn’t complete this so skipped to:

Expert:
33:10 Diamond Mine
36:01 LadderLand II
36:46 Indiana Who?
39:41 Stair Crazy
41:18 House of Horrors
42:11 The Quest Begins!
43:55 Quest 2 – The Dread Keep
45:22 Quest 3 – The Dungeon!
47:44 Quest 4 – Caverns of Yig! 
(Lovecraft influence?)
49:06 Quest 5 – Devil’s Maze

Expansion Pack:
50:04 The Forgotten City
50:58 Aeropics
51:40 Great Balls of Fire
52:13 Stairway to Heaven
55:18 WHERE AM I?
56:46 Rat Mountain
57:38 Roller Derby
58:37 Bats In The Belfry
59:33 Devil’s Doom
1:00:47 Here Comes The Tax Men
1:01:21 Rock ‘n’ Roll
1:01:57 WITCH CAT ??
1:04:18 Pyro-mid

1:05:50 Oh Hail!
1:07:07 MISSION IMPOSSIBLE
1:09:52 The Graveyard
1:11:48 The Yellow Brick Road
1:12:41 Insect King
1:13:58 Dark Tower
1:14:34 Totally Tubular
1:16:07 Slidely Annoying
1:16:49 Treasure Island
1:18:14 Necropolis
1:18:56 Maze Master
1:21:53 Key Slime Pie
1:23:27 Shadows & Spectres
1:24:43 FIRE ESCAPE!
1:27:15 T-Time
1:28:20 Wizard Blizzard
1:28:48 Burning Bridges
1:29:54 Haunted Castle
1:30:48 Condo from HELL!
1:33:02 The Golden Gate

1:35:16 ‘Tons’ of Elevators

1:36:51 Cast Spell When Falling
1:37:16 It's the Pits!
